OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmum died following benefit 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ferrors                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The family of a mother who died after a
OL,6, series of errors with her benefits has 
OL,7, agreed a "substantial settlement".     
OL,9,FPhilippa Day, 27, was found collapsed  
OL,10,Fat her Nottingham home with a letter   
OL,11,Frejecting an assessment in August 2019.
OL,13,FAn inquest heard the way her claim was 
OL,14,Fdealt with was the "predominant factor"
OL,15,Fin her overdose.                       
OL,17,FThe family said the settlement would   
OL,18,Fprovide for Miss Day's son, but that   
OL,19,Fnothing can "put right the wrong that  
OL,20,Fcontributed to Philippa's death".      
